 1999-16171999-09-280,  HERITAGE,  ,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of PATTI PACHOLEK, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Leon Frederick Loucks, whose term has expired.
